[32m +# Family Echo - Digital Family Legacy Website[m
[32m +[m
[32m +A beautiful, interactive digital archive designed to celebrate and preserve family memories, profiles, and voices. Make your family "alive online" with emotional, accessible, and engaging content.[m
[32m +[m
[32m +## 🌟 Features[m
[32m +[m
[32m +### Core Functionality[m
[32m +- **Family Profiles**: Detailed member profiles with photos, bios, hobbies, and voice recordings[m
[32m +- **Memory Gallery**: Photo, video, audio, and text memories with tagging and filtering[m
[32m +- **Interactive Family Tree**: Visual family tree with zoom, search, and member details[m
[32m +- **Voice Memories**: Audio clips for preserving family voices and stories[m
[32m +- **Memorial Profiles**: Special tribute sections for deceased family members[m
[32m +- **Search & Filter**: Advanced search across all content with multiple filter options[m
[32m +[m
[32m +### User Experience[m
[32m +- **Responsive Design**: Beautiful on desktop, tablet, and mobile devices[m
[32m +- **Accessibility**: High-contrast mode, keyboard navigation, and screen reader support[m
[32m +- **Smooth Animations**: Framer Motion animations for engaging interactions[m
[32m +- **Breadcrumb Navigation**: Easy navigation with clear page hierarchy[m
[32m +- **Loading States**: Elegant loading indicators and transitions[m
[32m +[m
[32m +### Visual Design[m
[32m +- **Warm Color Palette**: Soft blue (#4A90E2), cream (#FFF8E7), and gold (#FFD700)[m
[32m +- **Typography**: Lora (serif) for headings, Roboto (sans-serif) for body text[m
[32m +- **Polaroid Frames**: Nostalgic photo styling with subtle rotations[m
[32m +- **Card-based Layout**: Clean, organized content presentation[m
[32m +- **Custom Animations**: Fade-in effects and smooth transitions[m
[32m +[m
