[32m +## 🔧 Customization[m
[32m +[m
[32m +### Adding New Family Members[m
[32m +1. Edit the `FamilyContext.js` file[m
[32m +2. Add member data to the `initialState.members` array[m
[32m +3. Include photo URL, bio, hobbies, and relationship[m
[32m +[m
[32m +### Styling Changes[m
[32m +1. Modify `tailwind.config.js` for design system changes[m
[32m +2. Update `src/index.css` for global styles[m
[32m +3. Use Tailwind classes for component-specific styling[m
[32m +[m
[32m +### Adding New Pages[m
[32m +1. Create new component in `src/pages/`[m
[32m +2. Add route to `src/App.js`[m
[32m +3. Update navigation in `src/components/Navbar.js`[m
